title: Dev (#57)
message:
Dev (#57)

* updated all dependencies except reagent
added warn-on-infer flag
added infer-externs compiler flag

* fix: bbox now can deal with points in feature and geometry collections

* expound added for human-readable spec explanations
REFACTOR: subs -> subscriptions
fetch/json now takes a keyword as handler and dispatches an event on success
map related functions moved to mapbox
cosmetic changes

* prefer case for literal value comparison

* added photon as a geocoding engine to fallback when mapbox fails

* removed useless icons

* added toast capabilities

* fix: event-fx handlers should return an effect map not a new cofx
fix: dont compute uri on nil position
cosmetic changes

* footer element added

* directions screen created with trip information
cosmetic changes

* fix: the top and down padding need to increase due to header and footer
fix: map/bound is an effect not an event

* fix: expound is required for prod-build

* added extra information to the trip details

* store user input on change

* ops forgot to omit this one

* report mapbox geocoding misses
add provider to geocoding results
fix: transform firebase data to js
fix: dont show directions if the user searched for nothing

* display turn by turn instructions in the app

* replace search icon by clear when text is present
press clear icon to remove text input

* prefer walking instructions over driving instructions for comparison
make trip details footer prettier

* prettified directions with card item

* added internet state listener

* fix: bug in expound library

* floating gps button added
display error screen on unknown position
move camera to user position otherwise
cosmetic changes
added images for error screens

* fetch init.json file from local disk not remotely
avoid splash screen to directly to home
gitignore cosmetic changes

* fix: prevent crash on connectivity change - update mapbox version (not yet officially released)

* fix: upgrated native-base to solve fab issue
cosmetic changes
